Planned functionality


Near term:

1. Twitter integration
2. Set list of topics
3. Retweet tweets tagged with that topic every 30 mins
4. Read data from hackernews, based on ame topics of interest list
5. Shorten url of these topics and tweet every hour

Long term:

1. follow back users who followed you
2. check list of followers if somebody unfollows you, unfollow them back (will have to chekc feasibility)
3. read tweets addressed to account and reply back based on NLP (use GPT 3 or some middleware from amazom/google)
